text: Lachendorf is a collective municipality in Celle, in Lower Saxony, Germany. Its seat is in Lachendorf. The Samtgemeinde Lachendorf has the following municipalities: # Ahnsbeck # Beedenbostel # Eldingen # Hohne # Lachendorf Category:Samtgemeinden in Lower Saxony Category:Celle (district)
